    <title>Christian Aid Global</title>
    <description>Today 1.3 billion people live in extreme poverty. Tonight 900 million will go to bed hungry. Yet our world has never been richer. 

Christian Aid believes that poverty can and must be ended.  Listen to regular podcasts from the Communications Team at Christian Aid as we meet the people and see the work that is transforming the lives of poor people in more than 60 countries around the world. 

To find out more, visit www.christianaid.org.uk or follow us on Twitter @CA_global.

Leave us a message by using the record button below or by calling:

0118 413 8274
</description>
